account.descriptionLink:
Are you ready to permanently lock two-sided liquidity in Meteora’s 1-2% pool to support the movement and earn from fees—the (3,3) way?
I’m currently evaluating how many core contributors we can bring together to determine if this is a path worth pursuing. Let’s build something sustainable. Dynamic pool link with ability to permanently lock: https://app.meteora.ag/pools/create
account.name: Meteora Permanently locked two-sided liquidity test proposal for RYOSHI.
